Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}是啊，我还真有眼光选了他{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I sure know how to pick them.{\r}
