Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:52.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}这样吧，我陪你走回家{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Hey,tell you what,let me walk you home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:57.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我们去每个报摊 烧掉所有的时报和邮报{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}We'll stop by every newsstand and burn every copy of The Times and The Post.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}为什么要烧邮报？ 你没看邮报？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-Why The Post?. -You didn't see The Post?.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}没有，你看了？ 没有，怎么了？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-No. You? -No. Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:13.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}那些剧评真的是在嫉妒我？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You really think these newspapers are just jealous of me?{\r}
