Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我知道，所以他们才攻击我{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I know. That's why they trashed me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}等一下 怎么了？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-Wait. Wait a minute. -What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我实在搞不懂你{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't get you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你先是讨厌我{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I mean,first you hate me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:40.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}然后跟我上床{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Then you sleep with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}然后你又跟我撇清关系 现在又想要我了？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Then you want nothing to do with me. Now you want me again?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你没跟女演员约过会吗？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You never went out with an actress before?{\r}
