Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}当然喜欢 那你为什么拒绝我？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-Of course I do. -So how come you blew me off?{\r}
