Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我总是要挑那个最聪明的…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I always have to pick,like,the smartest guy...{\r}
