Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:16.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}谢了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks.{\r}
