Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}来，把你的脚抬上来{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Here we go. Let's get your feet up there.{\r}
