Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:09.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我把桶子放在这里 免得你想吐{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm gonna put this can right here in case you have to hurl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:20.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}请不要挂断 我们很重视您的来电{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Please stay on the line. Your call is very important to us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你已经24小时没睡了 去睡吧{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You've been up for 24 hours. Go to sleep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:26.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}这样很不健康{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}This isn't healthy.{\r}
