Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:32.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你知道为什么？ 因为我吃了核黄素{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}And you know why? Because of all the riboflavin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}这是昨晚那套衣服{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Didn't you have that on last night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:42.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我在凯特家过夜 但是什么也没做{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I stayed at Kate's but nothing happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:48.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}是啊，上次我在彼特那里我们也只是看了一部电影 我们的…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Yeah, last time l was at Pete's we just watched a movie...of us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}之前做爱的电影{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}...that we'd made earlier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:56.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}很抱歉，我控制不住，我有男朋友了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}l'm sorry, l can't help it.l have a boyfriend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你怎么没来？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Hey,where were you?{\r}
