Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:06.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你的戏对我们很重要 谢谢你的等候{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I swear,your play is very important to us. Thank you for your patience.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:10.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我接下来将去看你的戏{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Your play is the next play I'm gonna see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你跟凯特怎么样？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}How'd it go with Kate?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:14.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}感觉好棒{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}It was great!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:19.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我陪她走回家 我们之间心有灵犀{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I walked her home,and it was amazing how much we connected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}后来她昏过去了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Then she passed out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}但是等她醒来{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}But then she woke up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我们聊了一整晚{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}And we stayed up all night talking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我们现在为彼此疯狂{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}And now we're crazy about each other!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你经历了关键性的夜晚{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You had "the night"!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}当两个人发现他们坠入爱河{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}When two people realize their feelings for each other...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}他们会聊上很久 弄清楚对方的一切{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}...and they talk for hours and learn all about the other person.{\r}
