Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你了解她的家庭了吗？ 两个兄弟，一个死了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-Did you learn about her family? -Two brothers. One died!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}漂亮！{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}这是吧台那位女士请的{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}This is from the woman at the bar.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:01.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}对不起，她认错人了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Sorry. She thought you were somebody else.{\r}
